name: #TRASHimal Raccoon, Name of: Sidney the Scavenger
description: Hey there, little buddy! Would you like the rest of my sandwich? Meet Sidney, he's an excellent scavenger who's as gentle as can be. Just don't cross his pack or threaten his kits. Welcome to the #TRASHimals Celebration of 2021. This is my first piece for the event, created as a gift to the wonderful community. I will be airdropping one edition to everyone who participates in celebrating #TRASHimals art in the month of May 2021.
